It was the wedding everyone was waited for. On December 31, Nonhlanhla Soldaat and Hector Mkansi had their dream day. The couple's love story warmed hearts after a video of Mkansi proposing in a KFC at the Vaal went viral. Soon enough, they had pledges and sponsors pouring in for their wedding. Here's a look at their dreamy day. Here's what else happened on the big day.